OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy at first in the morning
OL,6,Fwith a few showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FTurning drier through the day with
OL,8,Fincreasing amounts of sunshine.
OL,9,FFeeling much fresher than recent days.
OL,10,FRather breezy particularly across high
OL,11,Fground.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry and sunny into the
OL,14,Fevening, with clear spells overnight,
OL,15,Fcloud increasing from the west towards
OL,16,Fdawn. Much cooler than recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
