OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FRather cloudy with some bright
OL,6,For sunny spells particularly across
OL,7,FCheshire and Lancashire during the
OL,8,Fmorning. Temperatures close to the
OL,9,Flate June average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FLargely dry with sunny spells next
OL,13,Fweek, but a few showers possible at
OL,14,Ftimes, particularly on Tuesday. Light
OL,15,Fwinds. Feeling pleasant in the
OL,16,Fsunshine with near normal temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
